502
00:39:29,146 --> 00:39:33,416
Grace, it’s important to know how to socialize when you’re in this business.

503
00:39:33,903 --> 00:39:35,198
Let’s have a drink.

504
00:39:36,557 --> 00:39:37,160
Just a little.

505
00:39:48,210 --> 00:39:48,970
You don’t want that?

506
00:40:03,204 --> 00:40:04,573
It’s alright. Don’t be afraid.

507
00:40:18,176 --> 00:40:19,865
Stop. Stop it!

508
00:40:21,508 --> 00:40:22,305
Who the hell are you?

509
00:40:23,625 --> 00:40:25,416
Don’t you dare do this to anyone again!

510
00:40:26,688 --> 00:40:27,416
Come on here!

511
00:40:29,568 --> 00:40:31,454
You jerk!

512
00:40:51,518 --> 00:40:52,272
Hello, Dad?

513
00:40:53,312 --> 00:40:54,576
I’ll fly back tonight.

514
00:41:05,555 --> 00:41:06,240
That jerk!

515
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:08,720
How could he do this to my daughter?

516
00:41:09,416 --> 00:41:10,957
I’m going to call the cops on him.

517
00:41:11,986 --> 00:41:13,213
Don’t do it, dear.

518
00:41:13,865 --> 00:41:15,388
You need to think this through.

519
00:41:20,230 --> 00:41:23,770
Where is Chadjen at a time like this?

520
00:41:24,352 --> 00:41:26,008
Where the hell has he gone?

521
00:41:27,388 --> 00:41:28,585
Forget him, Dad.

522
00:41:29,703 --> 00:41:31,773
My problem probably isn’t important enough for him.

523
00:41:39,601 --> 00:41:40,506
Not important enough for him?

524
00:41:40,912 --> 00:41:42,053
How could he do this?

525
00:41:43,321 --> 00:41:44,977
I trusted him to take care of you.

526
00:41:45,891 --> 00:41:47,586
But he let this happen to you!

527
00:42:00,677 --> 00:42:01,671
I’m sorry, dear.

528
00:42:03,727 --> 00:42:04,607
It’s alright now.

529
00:42:06,536 --> 00:42:08,059
It’s alright now, baby.

530
00:42:45,150 --> 00:42:47,266
Professor, I’ve made up my mind.

531
00:42:48,940 --> 00:42:50,619
I’ll take that job in the countryside.

532
00:42:51,094 --> 00:42:54,509
Nothing is more important than my promise to you, Som.

533
00:42:55,530 --> 00:42:56,306
Here.

534
00:42:59,111 --> 00:43:00,019
That’s adorable.

535
00:43:00,040 --> 00:43:00,770
(Team Shark Tao)

536
00:43:02,973 --> 00:43:04,377
Dad is in the hospital?

537
00:43:11,247 --> 00:43:11,911
Let’s go.

538
00:43:13,100 --> 00:43:16,383
If you go, just stay gone.

539
00:43:16,576 --> 00:43:18,065
Don’t come back to her.

540
00:43:18,454 --> 00:43:22,240
Once you know who New invited, you won’t be so happy.

541
00:43:22,285 --> 00:43:26,555
Oh, he brought a date.

542
00:43:26,671 --> 00:43:28,133
Hello, I’m Sue.

543
00:43:28,382 --> 00:43:29,874
I went to medical school with Chadjen.

544
00:43:34,110 --> 00:43:35,671
Oh, you don’t have to.

545
00:43:36,656 --> 00:43:37,780
Tao, take it easy.

546
00:43:38,168 --> 00:43:39,540
You forgot one other thing.

547
00:43:40,094 --> 00:43:40,847
What?
